data.description: PRICE IMPROVEMENT!!  Beautifully updated, well maintained brick home in the Weber/Schanen area. This home features a renovated Kitchen, spacious dining area, 4 bedrooms with walk-in closets, 2 full bathrooms.  Primary bedroom is off the kitchen and features a huge walk in closet with a large sitting area. Primary bathroom has an updated vanity with custom shelving. Windows in Primary have been replaced recently. Living room has a fireplace, freshly painted and sliding door w/built in blinds that open to back yard.  MUST SEE this great home in Carroll School District with a large backyard that is perfect for entertaining.
